Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.25,0:00:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music plays]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.45,0:01:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,ALLY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.76,0:01:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[console beeps]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.19,0:01:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[retina scanner beeps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.24,0:02:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-[buzzer]\N-Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.33,0:02:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] Oh, okay! Maybe the belt…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.25,0:02:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[buzzer]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.17,0:02:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] Huh? What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, looks like this system\Nis gonna take some getting used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.80,0:02:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How's this? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.22,0:02:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[door opens]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.39,0:02:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.31,0:02:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Did you get hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.78,0:02:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this? Kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.07,0:02:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh… I had a little fight\Nwith my wife, and…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.16,0:02:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that my daughter\Nis still young,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm hardly ever at home\Nas it is, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. It's probably best\Nif you sleep at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're gonna be missing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.25,0:02:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The rooms in this place are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were you, I'd just move\Nthe whole family in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:02:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, yeah,\Nthat's easy for you to say as a bachelor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-Where are they?\N-[Matsuda] Oh, they're on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.13,0:03:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Last we checked all of them\Nwere up in Misa-Misa's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.89,0:03:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] Surveillance cameras, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.56,0:03:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, since we know Misa has\Nsome connection to the Second Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it does make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.48,0:03:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But for God's sake, Matsuda,\Nwould you stop with this Misa-Misa crap?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] Oh… yeah. Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.28,0:03:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is gotta be\Nthe lamest date I've ever been on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, please. Just pretend\NI'm not even here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, are you gonna\Neat that piece of cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Cake makes you fat.\NI'm not gonna eat any.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I've found that you\Ndon't gain any weight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,as long as you burn calories\Nby using your brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Hm! So now\Nyou're calling me stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine then. I'll give you the piece of cake
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,as long as you agree\Nto leave me and Light alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.17,0:03:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I leave you two alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.88,0:03:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still gonna be watching\Non surveillance cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.01,0:03:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-So, it wouldn't make any difference.\N-You pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.64,0:03:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you stop\Nwith your creepy hobby?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You can call me whatever you like.\NLast chance for cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.44,0:03:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just close the curtains\Nand turn off the lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.61,0:03:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] We have infrared cameras\Nin here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Misa groans]\N-What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought moving here\Nwas supposed to help us catch Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but since we've been here\Nyou don't seem all that motivated to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] Not motivated?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Depressed? What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, hmm…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Truthfully, all this time,\NI thought that you were Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and my entire case\Nhinged on that fact. [gulps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I just can't get past the fact\Nthat my deduction was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, having said that,\NI'm still suspicious of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we're wearing these.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And we also know\NKira can control people's actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means it's highly likely
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that Kira was controlling your actions\Nso that I would suspect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If I assume both you and Misa\Nwere being controlled by him,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,then everything we've observed so far\Nmakes a lot more sense to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's what you think,\NMisa and I were both Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,during the time\Nwe were being controlled, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:04:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I could’ve been\Nwrong about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.09,0:05:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of you are Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[both] Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] If what I'm thinking is correct,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,when your confinement began\Nyou were Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it's coincidence\Nthat as soon as you were in prison
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,all the killing stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then, everything\Npointed to you being Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but after two weeks,\Ncriminals actually began dying again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,KIRA RETURNS
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.53,0:05:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on that evidence,\NI can only conclude that…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira's power passes between people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an interesting idea.\NBut if it's true,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.91,0:05:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll be nearly impossible for us\Nto catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That's why I'm overwhelmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we catch someone\Nunder his control,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll likely lose their powers\Nand any memory of their crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in the end,\Npursuing them becomes futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But at this point we have no way\Nof knowing if that's the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.77,0:05:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, would ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"Cheer up"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.73,0:05:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm sorry, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:06:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably better\Nif I just stop trying so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,By chasing Kira so desperately
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,we're just putting our lives at risk\Nfor nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Ryuzaki grunts]\N-[Misa screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Ryuzaki and Light grunting]\N-[objects clatter]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Misa moans]\N-[Ryuzaki groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, that really hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.\NYou don't feel like doing anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,just because your genius deduction\Nwas wrong and I'm not Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki grunts] Fine.\NPerhaps I phrased it the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant it would be pointless for us\Nto make a move,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,so we shouldn't even bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't chase Kira,\Nhe will never be caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you want?\NIf you were just gonna give up,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,then why did you involve\Nall those innocent people?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, what was the point\Nof putting Misa and me behind bars?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:07:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, whatever the reason…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Ryuzaki grunts]\N-[Misa screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.71,0:07:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,…an eye for an eye, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[both scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Ryuzaki and Light grunting]\N-Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.94,0:07:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki grunts]\NIt's not my deduction that was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact is, I can say
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.02,0:07:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that Light Yagami is Kira and\NMisa Amane is the Second Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but it won't be enough\Nto solve the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why I'm a little depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.78,0:07:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is that so unreasonable?\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.16,0:07:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.\NBesides, you should hear yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as if you won't be satisfied\Nunless I'm Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I… I won't be satisfied\Nunless you're Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there may be some truth to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.92,0:07:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, now that you mention it,\Nyou're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I wanted you to be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:07:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:08:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said before, an eye for an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a lot stronger than I look, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to call the room and stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.03,0:08:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-[phone ringing]\N-[both] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes?\N-[Matsuda] Ryuzaki, I've got good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa-Misa is number one
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,in Eighteen Magazine's reader\Npopularity poll!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] And get this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gonna get a lead role\Nin Nishinaka's next movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsuda's acting stupid again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.75,0:08:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[line beeping]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Well, that is his specialty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,TWO MONTHS LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're not feeling up to it,\Nbut come over here for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a close look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-It can't be coincidence.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] All of them were prominent\NJapanese businessmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.24,0:08:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,CEOs whose companies are leaders\Nin their respective industries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In just over a month\Nthey all died of heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected, there's been\Na general downturn in the market.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,With the exception of Yotsuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.33,0:09:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,their deaths have worked\Nin Yotsuba's favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.25,0:09:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking back,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,there have been 13 similar deaths\Nin the past three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Your thoughts?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on this I can only conclude\Nthat Kira is supporting Yotsuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.56,0:09:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. It could be.\NBut if what you're saying is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,we can assume that punishing criminals\Nis not this Kira's real intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.15,0:09:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Right
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Punishing criminals\Nis a diversion for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.65,0:09:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It obscures the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that he is actually killing people\Nfor the benefit of his company.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.61,0:09:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you…\Nfeeling a bit more motivated now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[man 1] It's funny.\NThis is starting to feel too easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.43,0:10:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at all we've done\Nand no one suspects a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[man 2] Our stock continues to increase\Nbut we've kept it below the radar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[man 1] Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything appears to be proceeding\Naccording to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true. However, there is one thing\Nthat has me concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.07,0:10:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Those three we had killed last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did all of them die of heart attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.58,0:10:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we agreed\None would be accidental.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.58,0:10:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite right. We did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.33,0:10:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem was that we named\Na specific location in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, he wasn't even here when he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear he and his mistress\Nwere in Italy at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.09,0:10:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If our request\Nis physically impossible then…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira will kill that person\Nusing his default method. A heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like I was saying last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.35,0:10:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want it to look believable,\Nrequest accidental death or disease
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.06,0:10:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and Kira will always find\Nthe quickest way to make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, given Kira's history,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.98,0:10:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the police are probably\Nstill focused on the dying criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.11,0:11:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite frankly, if someone was able
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to trace the deaths of these people\Nback to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,then he would have to be a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, we've taken precautions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hm?\N-Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.29,0:11:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Chief! Oh, you too, Mogi!\NI've got some great news.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.75,0:11:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not even sure how he figured it out,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but Light has a theory that Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is somehow involved\Nwith the Yotsuba Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.97,0:11:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yotsuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh… yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.93,0:11:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's probably it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-Good work.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.68,0:11:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We just spoke with the director
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.39,0:11:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and it seems Kira has offered bribes\Nto a number of politicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs] Kira made an offer…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as the NPA agrees\Nnot to pursue him anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,he won't lay a hand on any politicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.91,0:11:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's that.\NThe police caved into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[all gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mogi and I have already\Nmade up our minds on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Aizawa, Matsuda…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.50,0:11:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,if you wish to continue working this case,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:12:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll have to hand in\Nyour letter of resignation to the NPA.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as Mogi and I are going to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[both gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.55,0:12:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Like it or not, you cannot pursue Kira\Nas member of the police force anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha… Hold-- Hold on a second, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They made it quite clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you continue to work with L\Nyou will be fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.56,0:12:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So then, Chief, you're gonna…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.28,0:12:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In a few hours,\NI'm no longer going to be your chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,However, we all have our own lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.99,0:12:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So, think it over carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.24,0:12:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.87,0:12:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially, if you've got family\Nto support.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[breathes heavily]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] If you want my opinion,\Nyou'd be better off as police officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] I was alone\Nwhen I started this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And although I'm grateful to all of you\Nfor staying with me as long as you have,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.18,0:12:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that I can do this by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be sure to visit you\Nat the department
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and bring you Kira's head as a reward\Nfor all that you've sacrificed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.02,0:12:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I'm alive,\Nyou won't be working alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-You have my word on that!\N-[chain rattles]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] Hm. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.07,0:13:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have Light working with me\Nuntil I catch Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,so I won't be alone after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But as I said, I think the rest of you\Nshould remain as police officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But when you first contacted us,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you said that you'd need the help\Nof the police in order to solve this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] That's because the police\Nas an organization,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,were still hoping to arrest Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They weren't bowing to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, with all due respect,\Nthere's a big difference
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,between the help of two or three civilians\Nand the police as an organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm. And as you said,\Nthe police have made their position clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't wanna catch Kira,\Nso let's just leave it at that. [swallows]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.73,0:13:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose what you're saying\Nmakes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If we are not police officers anymore,\Nwe won't be of much use to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.11,0:13:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,However, we're all\Npersonally involved in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.95,0:13:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All of us have risked our lives\Nto catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.66,0:13:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that give us the right to decide
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,whether we stay here\Nor return to the police force?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.16,0:13:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then by all means, please,\Nmake your decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Chief, wait. If you quit your job\Nwith the police force,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll be unemployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we do catch Kira,\Nwhat are you gonna do after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.63,0:14:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Matsuda] Oh…\N-After that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I hadn't really thought of it,\Nbut I suppose after we catch Kira…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to dust off my resume.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Count me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.48,0:14:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna quit the police\Nand chase Kira too, Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And I still have my job\Nas Misa-Misa's manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, if I stayed on\Nas a police officer,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd feel like a total loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.53,0:14:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] Think before you open\Nyour mouth, Matsuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.12,0:14:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.95,0:14:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any way I could still keep my job\Nand help you in my spare time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.63,0:14:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs] There isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.47,0:14:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you remain a police officer,\Nthen please, don't come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.51,0:14:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know I won't leak any information.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.35,0:14:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be sharing any of our information.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.85,0:14:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.85,0:15:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You are free to pursue Kira on your own,\Nif you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.44,0:15:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't think\Nit's fair to your families
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,to burden them by giving up\Nyour livelihood just to continue this…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.03,0:15:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see how that's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.41,0:15:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as Ryuzaki says,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,no one here is gonna blame you\Nfor quitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.95,0:15:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We all understand why you gotta do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.54,0:15:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Chief has a family, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.71,0:15:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Our situations are completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs] Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,To leave now\Nafter all we have been through…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.38,0:15:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I was prepared to die\Nif that's what it took to catch him
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.51,0:15:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and I meant it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of friend would I be to Ukita\Nif I quit now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I became a detective,\Nso I could catch the bad guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,not run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[Watari] Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Early on in the investigation,\Nyou specifically told me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.99,0:15:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that if a task force member\Nwere to lose their job,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.36,0:15:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,under any circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.86,0:15:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I should make preparations to ensure
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.62,0:15:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that their family's financial future\Nwas secured.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:16:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you recall, a trust was set aside\Nfor that very purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.33,0:16:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little curious as to why\Nyou're withholding this information?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-[gasps]\N-This is not the time or place, Watari.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.17,0:16:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[Watari] I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! So, all this time\Nwe had nothing to worry about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.34,0:16:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you did that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.01,0:16:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go, Aizawa.\NIsn't that a great news?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.26,0:16:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki,\NI assume that was some kind of test
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to determine how committed I was\Nto this task force.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It-- It-- It's not like that, Aizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki's just not the type\Nto say things directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.57,0:16:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know that by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.24,0:16:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.45,0:16:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Ryuzaki] No.\N-[all] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.41,0:16:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] I was testing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.99,0:16:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to see\Nwhich one you would choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oh.\N-Ryuzaki…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[breathes forcefully]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine then!\NIf I wasn't sure before, I am now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.51,0:16:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But Aizawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's face it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.63,0:16:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't able to decide right away,\Nlike you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.09,0:16:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I was leaning towards\Ngoing back to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Aizawa. Don't be so stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] No! I quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.48,0:17:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I know this for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.98,0:17:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always hated Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate him and his way of doing things!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.40,0:17:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] That's too bad,\Nbecause I like you, Aizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.37,0:17:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[growls quietly]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.53,0:17:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I also hate the way\Nyou've always gotta have the last word!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.04,0:17:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You insult me\Nand now you say something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! I am outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.33,0:17:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[door opens]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[door closes]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.30,0:17:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I just found another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.93,0:17:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A general manager of a bank,\NYotsuba's biggest competitor,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.35,0:17:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,on September 7th, he slipped and fell\Non the front steps of his house and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] September 7th was a Friday,\Nwasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light and Ryuzaki] Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,After going over this again,\NI noticed something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.49,0:17:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All the deaths\Nwhich are beneficial to Yotsuba,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:18:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,are concentrated around the weekends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.58,0:18:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? On the weekends?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,With the first few victims
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.12,0:18:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the time of death\Nappears to have been random,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.21,0:18:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,More recently they all take place between\NFriday night and Saturday afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.84,0:18:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm amazed\Nthat you even noticed that, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsuda, I thought I told you\Nto stop calling me "Chief."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.88,0:18:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry,\Nbut you'll always be the Chief to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.01,0:18:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a really important clue, Dad.\NNice work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, I can't let myself\Nfall behind you and Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, the last thing I want\Nis to be dead weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. "Dead weight"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.73,0:18:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] Is Kira someone from Yotsuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is Kira simply using Yotsuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.15,0:18:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't figured that out yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.61,0:18:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but we will proceed under the assumption\Nthat this is Kira's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We will focus on Yotsuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.66,0:18:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts] This is all\Nof the Yotsuba Group's employees.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.75,0:18:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] That's 300,000 people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How did he put this together so quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing, Mogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.84,0:18:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] He's been incredibly efficient\Nfrom the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, tell me, is there anything\NI can do to help with the investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.14,0:19:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides the manager thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.26,0:19:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] So, you really wanna be useful?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.85,0:19:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] Then could you get me\Nanother cup of coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.02,0:19:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.69,0:19:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] And for our guests\Nover there as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.57,0:19:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.19,0:19:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a sec. Who let them in?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.86,0:19:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two are the newest members\Nof the task force.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.08,0:19:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The name's Aiber.\NI'm a conman. How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.71,0:19:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Wedy. And I'm a thief by trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. A conman and a thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.96,0:19:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Aiber is a lifelong conman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.47,0:19:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,His unparalleled social skills
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.76,0:19:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,allow him to befriend\Nand gain the trust of any target.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll use him for infiltration.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.52,0:19:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,As for Wedy,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.68,0:19:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,she is a thief who specializes\Nin cracking high-end security systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.23,0:19:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,As proof of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,she was able to enter the building\Nwithout setting off a single alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.57,0:20:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You expect us to work with criminals?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,However, these two\Nhave never once been caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's unlikely\Nthey'll be killed by Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of them\Nas professionals of the underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.12,0:20:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,To investigate Yotsuba,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,we're gonna need the help\Nof people like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.75,0:20:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all do our part\Nand make this happen, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yeah!\N-Yeah. Deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[girl laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-Huh?\N-[giggles] Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.11,0:20:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yumi…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.65,0:20:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Eriko…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.03,0:20:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?\NShouldn't you be at work right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to tell me\Nif you're planning to be home for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.66,0:20:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I just went shopping\Nand I only bought for me and Yumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.29,0:20:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can eat my dinner\Nand I'll have dessert instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.33,0:20:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It was sort of a last-minute decision,\Nbut they just gave me some time off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:20:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is a "time off" a vacation, Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.75,0:21:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.55,0:21:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yippee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on,\NI can have a break every single week.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.64,0:21:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I can go with you to the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.39,0:21:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[trembling]\NMaybe we can go to the zoo together,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,or the amusement park…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.36,0:21:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh. What's wrong, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.28,0:21:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yumi] Mommy, why is Daddy crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.57,0:21:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED